==  Ghana Manpanyin Yere firi bre a wonyaa fahodie ==
Ghana Manpanyin Yere yɛ edin a wɔde to manpanyin a ɔte agua so mprenpren no yere.<ref>First Ladies | The Presidency of The Republic of Ghana (archive.org)</ref> Manpanyin Yere a ɔte so mprenpren din de Rebecca Akufo-Addo, a ɔhyɛɛ  ase kura dibea yi firi afe 2017. Wontua won ka nanso, Ghana manpyin Yere ne won abediakyire yɛ nea wɔma wɔn sika kakra a wɔde bɛtotɔ ntaadeɛ, sɛnea ɛbɛma w'atumi ahyɛ Ghana amamerɛ ahorɔw no mu kena denam wɔn ntaadehyɛ mu.
